# GSD / Planning
# .planning/ is mostly local working notes (intel, codebase maps, research,
# session artefacts). backlog/ is the exception — those scoping docs are
# durable team-visible artefacts, so re-include them explicitly. Everything
# else at .planning/ root that should be tracked (PROJECT.md, ROADMAP.md,
# STATE.md, REQUIREMENTS.md, phases/*) was force-added once and stays tracked
# because .gitignore doesn't affect already-indexed files.
.planning/*
!.planning/backlog/
!.planning/backlog/**
graphify-out/

